 6249:                          ;
 6250:                          ; This is a complete BCD floating point 
 6251:                          ; controller. It provides 8 digits of ac
 6252:                          ; range from +127 to -127. The mantissa 
 6253:                          ; exponent is expressed in pseudo-twos c
 6254:                          ; is used to express the number ZERO. An
 6255:                          ; greater than means the exponent is pos
 6256:                          ; 81H = E+1, 82H = E+2 and so on. If the
 6257:                          ; the exponent is negative, 7FH = E-1, 7
 6258:                          ; ALL NUMBERS ARE ASSUMED TO BE NORMALIZ
 6259:                          ; normalized after calculation. A normal
 6260:                          ; <=.99999999.
 6261:                          ;
 6262:                          ; The numbers in memory assumed to be st

