 6267:                          ; DIGIT 56 OF ARGUMENT 2   =   VALUE OF 
 6268:                          ; DIGIT 34 OF ARGUMENT 2   =   VALUE OF 
 6269:                          ; DIGIT 12 OF ARGUMENT 2   =   VALUE OF 
